ŕIn Memory of Kiran Patel (9th August 1950- 1st June 2011)
A selfless friend to the community, gentleman and much missed newsagent,
who served Bickley with distinction for more than 30 years. His sense of
humour, unerring dedication and outstanding service will be greatly missed.
Dedicated by the friends and customers of Kiran
